data.description: Immediate possession of this 2-story home!  Move-in ready 3 bedroom 2 1/2 bath home with an attached 2 car garage.  Low maintenance on this Jagoe home.  Large corner lot with a nice back patio for grilling.  Laundry room conveniently located upstairs with all bedrooms.  Walk-in closets in each bedroom with an additional living area upstairs.  As you enter the main level you will find a formal living room separated from the main living room and kitchen/dining room.  Great price for the square footage!
